snippet.title: Rabbit in the clouds - PlayStation 4 Gameplay
snippet.description:
A small game where you control a rabbit escaping from the darkness that is chasing him.
You need to jump on clouds to progress and use soap bubbles to jump even higher.
During the game, you can encounter several types of power-up bonuses to gain a temporary advantage.

Developed by Xitilon
